original: Dalgren, Gunnar Kristian, hypo-teksdirektör, Växjö, f. 2/8/9-7 i Höganäs, Malmöh. 1., av kamr. Gustaf D. o. Selma Lundberg. G. 31 m. Karin Palmgren. Barn: Ulla Ingegärd Birgitta f. 33, Bertil Gunnar 38. — Stud:-ex. i Hälsingborg 16, jur. kand. i Lund 21. E. o. not. i hovr. över Skåne o. Blek. 21, tingstjg. i Ingelstads o. Jär-restads doms. 22-24, anst. h. Smål. m. fl. provinsers hypoteksfören. fr. 24, bitr. omb :man 27, andre dito 38, verk-st. dir. o. förste omb :man sed. 44. V. auditör 41-44, äger fastigh. i Växjö, överförmynd., v. ordf. i brandslyr. o. polisndn i Växjö, suppl. i styr. f. Smål. m. fl. provinsers hypoteksfören. sed. 44.
translated: Dalgren, Gunnar Kristian, hypo-mortgage director, Växjö, b. 2/8/9-7 in Höganäs, Malmöhus. Son of Kamr. Gustaf D. and Selma Lundberg. Married in 1931 to Karin Palmgren with two children: Ulla Ingegärd Birgitta b. 1933 and Bertil Gunnar b. 1938. He passed the studentexamen exam in Hälsingborg in 1916 and graduated in law from Lund University in 1921. He served as a Deputy Notary in the Court of Appeal for Skåne and Blekinge from 1921, worked as a judge in Ingelstad and Järrestad's district courts from 1922 to 1924, and worked in several provincial mortgage companies in Småland province from 1924 as an assistant secretary, and from 1944 as the Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer. He also served as an auditor from 1941 to 1944, owned a property in Växjö, and was Deputy Chairman of the Board for the Växjö Fire Brigade and Police Commissioner since 1944. He was also a member of the Board of Directors of several provincial mortgage companies in Småland province from 1944.
